README is a file that descripts whatever files that I have to submit on CCLE.

lab4c_tcp.c is a source file that can run with beagle bone and tcp socket to see what the temperature is right now at a certain place. 

lab4c_tls.c is a source file that can run with beagle bone and tcp socket with secure transfer data to see what the temperature is right now at a certain place. 

LOGFILE is just a log file that contain everything output if the server uses log option.
 
Makefile 
	 default: make the source file into a runnable file
	 clean: clean the file created by Makefile
	 dist: create the deliverable tarball